<div id="review_665261660" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/665261660" />
    <a title="Kimberly" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/17371689-kimberly"><img alt="Kimberly" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1404147069p2/17371689.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/665261660?book_show_action=true">Jul 11, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Kimberly" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Kimberly" href="/user/show/17371689-kimberly">Kimberly</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="ebook " href="/book/show/10972687-the-wide-game">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/17371689-kimberly?shelf=shelfari-group-read">shelfari-group-read</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer665261660" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9402590385934662535">Harmony, Indiana: This was technically the first book Michael West based in this town besieged by otherworldly influences. I read the three novels out of order, but that did nothing to take away from the plot of any. Each novel is a stand alone, and each will have you eagerly searching out more stories from Harmony. The Wide Game takes place in the 80&apos;s, in a cornfield ruled by unseen energies. When these elements decide to play, there isn&apos;t anywhere that&apos;s safe....<br/><br/>Recommended!</span>
  <span id="freeText9402590385934662535" style="display:none">Harmony, Indiana: This was technically the first book Michael West based in this town besieged by otherworldly influences. I read the three novels out of order, but that did nothing to take away from the plot of any. Each novel is a stand alone, and each will have you eagerly searching out more stories from Harmony. The Wide Game takes place in the 80's, in a cornfield ruled by unseen energies. When these elements decide to play, there isn't anywhere that's safe....<br /><br />Recommended!</span>
  <a data-text-id="9402590385934662535" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


