        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3217300223" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10313300234926923916">I actually listened to this on Audible.com. This is a well woven book with many characters and circumstances as does happen in high school. 85% of this book tales place in the past of the main characters, however it’s so well written you fall into step without feeling the time jump. As the book leads you through this chilling tale of what happens during the Wide Game played back in those days. Amazing ending that shocks you and reminds you to be thankful for all you have! I definitely think this</span>
  <span id="freeText10313300234926923916" style="display:none">I actually listened to this on Audible.com. This is a well woven book with many characters and circumstances as does happen in high school. 85% of this book tales place in the past of the main characters, however it’s so well written you fall into step without feeling the time jump. As the book leads you through this chilling tale of what happens during the Wide Game played back in those days. Amazing ending that shocks you and reminds you to be thankful for all you have! I definitely think this is a book to be put on your to be read list and give it a bit of a bump up in the ranks you won’t be sorry! Great writing, fantastic characters!</span>
