              <span id="reviewTextContainer3172010732" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10840871310571400255">If your a fan of horror I highly recommend this series <br/>This manages to be creepy and gory satisfying all my needs<br/>Nila does a excellent job narrating <br/>Treat yourself and make this your next Listen <br/>I received a free review audiobook and voluntarily left this review</span>

          </span>
        </div>


